動作做6次<br />\n3.拎個兩公升壼裝1/3既糖，然後加入紅茶搞匀<br />\n4.用保鮮紙包好放入雪櫃冷凍<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;第二日&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n1.倒落杯度<br />\n2.加檸檬<br />\n<br />\n[熱檸茶]<br />\n1.煲紅茶<br />\n2.拎隻隔茶網出黎網住水壼，兩個水壼來回撞1次 = 1次，呢個動作做6次<br />\n3.倒落熱杯<br />\n4.加檸檬<br />\n<br />\n我見啲紅茶係一罐罐紅罐嘉頓Size既<br />\n<br />\n淨係記得呢啲步驟<br />\n利申當年做廚房佬，睇個水吧啊姐2日做一次呢個動作<br />\nSorry for 1999"},{"pid":"0ffbe298cda7fb08c21cb7baebe3e2f56188eb7c","tid":699745,"uid":3647,"like":5,"dislike":52,"score":-47,"quote":{"pid":"81ecc88b9f3ebc916e21834c06b79888deb2c08d","tid":699745,"uid":58321,"like":707,"dislike":17,"score":690,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T19:22:53.000Z","msg":"屌無個留言係有建設性，個撚個都小學雞懶好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 戇撚鳩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T20:23:39.000Z","msg":"你既建設性又係邊?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nLipton茶包8個 1.5L熱水"},{"pid":"4a5f8f5f025aa5557a0090d5fe1f404bf9a6640d","tid":699745,"uid":16668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T20:25:27.000Z","msg":"茶膽+水，分量自己倒倒下就知，加檸檬加冰，落小啲水落多啲冰，因為茶膽好熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"facef4e05a93f87298e0bf9574b298901124bc7a","tid":699745,"uid":58321,"like":60,"dislike":4,"score":56,"quote":{"pid":"0ffbe298cda7fb08c21cb7baebe3e2f56188eb7c","tid":699745,"uid":3647,"like":5,"dislike":52,"score":-47,"quote":{"pid":"81ecc88b9f3ebc916e21834c06b79888deb2c08d","tid":699745,"uid":58321,"like":707,"dislike":17,"score":690,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T19:22:53.000Z","msg":"屌無個留言係有建設性，個撚個都小學雞懶好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 戇撚鳩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T20:23:39.000Z","msg":"你既建設性又係邊?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nLipton茶包8個 1.5L熱水"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T20:42:38.000Z","msg":"入post唔可以係入黎學下點沖？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你話我入黎搞破壞就話"},{"pid":"b498946f3081cee937c27d7bd9e1a66665056f63","tid":699745,"uid":76848,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"98966b4b016