n一定要用紅茶<br />\n<br />\n利申 兩年水吧經驗"},{"pid":"c6c1c0840629d7b01d1051cf6a1b8bfddc3cf1e0","tid":699745,"uid":128600,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"81ecc88b9f3ebc916e21834c06b79888deb2c08d","tid":699745,"uid":58321,"like":707,"dislike":17,"score":690,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T19:22:53.000Z","msg":"屌無個留言係有建設性，個撚個都小學雞懶好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 戇撚鳩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T00:35:39.000Z","msg":"人地講咗你唔理解姐<br />\n<br />\n利申：為興趣學過"},{"pid":"338092a83cbc0357afae89b3862079bb086e50b8","tid":699745,"uid":5281,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"86fa28cd0f7d723fa14dab85100504fb394e9b1a","tid":699745,"uid":44787,"like":161,"dislike":1,"score":160,"quote":{"pid":"acbcd50bc8a3e34c8a3872b88d2f4c5741dd3188","tid":699745,"uid":43866,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"quote":{"pid":"2a053d16bd28bcab036f5e8eb2d7c5a1885f8c50","tid":699745,"uid":43850,"like":114,"dislike":1,"score":113,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T19:40:54.000Z","msg":"咩茶葉不是重點 反正間間唔同<br />\n重點超高溫煲茶 煲到酸<br />\n煲好要撞茶 你睇片d人拉到好高撞落去唔係扮型<br />\n係真係有用的 撞5-6次ok了<br />\n之後糖檸果d唔講了"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T19:54:10.000Z","msg":"屋企沖得唔好飲最主要係唔識煲茶<br />\n茶餐廳大部份都係用最下價既茶葉<br />\n如果好似水仙香片咁沖杯茶就晒鳩氣 倒左佢啦<br />\n識煲茶就算唔撞茶衰極有限 好似整蛋糕麵粉過唔過&rsquo;西&rsquo; 雖然層次唔同 但唔會衰得去邊"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T20:16:22.000Z","msg":"[凍檸茶]<br />\n<br />\n首先準備 :<br />\n一個兩L既水壺<br />\n糖<br />\n紅茶葉<br />\n檸檬酸切片<br />\n冰<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;前一晚&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n1.煲紅茶<br />\n2.拎隻隔茶網出黎網住水壼，兩個水壼來回撞1次 = 1次，呢個動作做6次<br />\n3.拎個兩公升壼裝1/3既糖，然後加入紅茶搞匀<br />\n4.用保鮮紙包好放入雪櫃冷凍<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;第二日&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n1.倒落杯度<br />\n2.加檸檬<br />\n<br />\n[熱檸茶]<br />\n1.煲紅茶<br />\n2.拎隻隔茶網出黎網住水壼，兩個水壼來回撞1次 = 1次，呢個動作做6次<br />\n3.倒落熱杯<br />\n4.加檸檬<br />\n<br />\n我見啲紅茶係一罐罐紅罐嘉頓Size既<br />\n<br />\n淨係記得呢啲步驟<br />\n利申當年做廚房佬，睇個水吧啊姐2日做一次呢個動作<br />\nSorry for 1999"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T00:38:45.000Z","msg":"凍0茶唔洗打咁多次，通常做奶茶膽先5到6次。0茶係打到第二/三次就要留岀黎，之後加糖，咁個茶就最清澈。凍奶茶就每日賣剩既茶放入雪櫃<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n淨係yellow label會重色，唔夠味咪信上面10幾包茶包沖埋一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d61985bd1c0c766eee9b0e870d101761e4a1e14a","tid":699745,"uid":6640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4268d5ac9f961f6cce99f79005079d90c98b4b6","tid":699745,"uid":74474,"like":175,"dislike":5,"score":170,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T19:06:18.000Z","msg":"16個Lipton 茶包沖成一壺茶"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T00:45:40.000Z","msg":"我以前暑期工係Lipton茶罐"},{"pid":"2d227f3ab04b97ae59f621096dd6e0cc3137d89e","tid":699745,"uid":173723,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T00:47:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"84db440bb013bfdbf704dc1b2bc10f303a4a9152","tid":699745,"uid":173723,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T00:49:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2d56be59980db1b292ef3363ddb9bed65b4e1859","tid":699745,"uid":4510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T01:04:49.000Z","msg":"之前返過暑期工 檸茶同奶茶都係用同一種茶 好似係捷榮既茶 檸茶就兩份茶 八份水 奶茶就七分茶 三分奶"},{"pid":"cbd7710b5c9a1b49ca3508232bbd9233e4ba5977","tid":699745,"uid":56953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84db440bb013bfdbf704dc1b2bc10f303a4a9152","tid":699745,"uid":173723,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T00:49:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T01:18:50.000Z","msg":"講緊#5果個回覆"},{"pid":"8280a8de169b48665cd963b0baff3af42d9234d0","tid":699745,"uid":1134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T01:32:05.000Z","msg":"教曉多你一樣野<br />\n奶茶個茶底雪一晚<br />\n第日再沖奶黎飲<br />\n正撚到仆街"},{"pid":"325f37ad59f75ba7e8a8589ab864e552ed03218b","tid":699745,"uid":43850,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ed294c86826166658408e4afd943b66f740e68db","tid":699745,"uid":13594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a053d16bd28bcab036f5e8eb2d7c5a1885f8c50","tid":699745,"uid":43850,"like":114,"dislike":1,"score":113,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T19:40:54.000Z","msg":"咩茶葉不是重點 反正間間唔同<br />\n重點超高溫煲茶 煲到酸<br />\n煲好要撞茶 你睇片d人拉到好高撞落去唔係扮型<br />\n係真係有用的 撞5-6次ok了<br />\n之後糖檸果d唔講了"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T23:57:08.000Z","msg":"超高溫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 9UP唔洗本 以為焗緊茶葉"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T01:42:48.000Z","msg":"唔識好似樓主咁不恥下問咪幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講完又唔撚信 正常人對沖茶認知係滖水焗茶<br />\n茶餐廳果d係煲幾分鐘迫晒d茶味出黎先好飲<br />\n利申:做過水吧"},{"pid":"555766b6e4faf7e40d9ddd8700d82b7043265d6f","tid":699745,"uid":190564,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T01:42:53.000Z","msg":"加多少少橙皮"},{"pid":"ec95f7afa7755a839823c707ddb49fe1c80efd36","tid":699745,"uid":70337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T01:43:32.000Z","msg":"以前做茶記檸茶好似係茶膽再溝水，比例1:1 <br />\n個茶色先透透地<br />\n奶茶就唔洗加水"},{"pid":"d3fa16cde5f41749279c0605451cb8fd144d58a9","tid":699745,"uid":147276,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T01:44:54.000Z","msg":"檸茶唔同茶膽 要溝水 <br />\n以前做機場呀鴻小吃水吧 year1 既時候<br />\n茶膽係整奶茶既 檸茶要溝1/3水<br />\n凍既話就完成左既茶膽加水 加糖<br />\n溶哂就等佢凍 通常都要第日先用到<br />\n<br />\n茶膽點整呢？ 我地用茶粉 落袋<br />\n用茶記既壺 茶記爐 <br />\n唔知咩爐黎 但茶記煲茶專用<br />\n滾左就回來拉3次 要高拉 撞茶撞走苦澀味<br />\nD泡就係撞哂出黎既空氣 茶會滑好多<br />\n拉完就再煲多3個字 再來回三次<br />\n咁就係茶膽  我一開始成日都撞到出哂界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 我果間成日有人外賣奶茶<br />\n因為都整得幾好飲 又認真教既<br />\n所以依家仲記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c60d1687dfcf2ec9312cb942a70637af22f8e45","tid":699745,"uid":131345,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T01:45:20.000Z","msg":"以前做一間英式酒吧果時因為有做lunch 所以學左(果間的做法)<br />\n我用舊式果種鐵壺 用熱水沖一次個壺(連埋個濾袋)<br />\n再落一個rock glass份量GE茶葉 加熱水到8-9分 撞佢4次 焗5-10分鐘(睇你急唔急用)<br />\n for客(用jar落7成冰 茶膽落4分1 再落熱水 )<br />\n for自己(用pint glass 7成冰 茶膽落6分1杯 再落熱水 再加糖水同檸檬)<br />\n<br />\n以前果度學係咁教 未必係正確做法 但個味唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c052a44e419ed3813a084b9ddade6ff7ed4736a7","tid":699745,"uid":79375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T01:49:38.000Z","msg":"我美心做過水吧時 : <br />\n(1) 先下2片檸檬<br />\n(2) 倒入八成滿的滾水<br />\n(3) 再加「2滴」濃縮紅茶葉沖出來的茶  (超濃茶味)<br />\n落 2滴有D 色就好了，太多會俾主任話<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fa59d63bf388cdd14fbffcbab9a773bb702c96d","tid":699745,"uid":90045,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"c052a44e419ed3813a084b9ddade6ff7ed4736a7","tid":699745,"uid":79375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T01:49:38.000Z","msg":"我美心做過水吧時 : <br />\n(1) 先下2片檸檬<br />\n(2) 倒入八成滿的滾水<br />\n(3) 再加「2滴」濃縮紅茶葉沖出來的茶  (超濃茶味)<br />\n落 2滴有D 色就好了，太多會俾主任話<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T01:55:39.000Z","msg":"唔怪得美心咁難飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a678fe68cd186194c467a52f4f99d14a224bb163","tid":699745,"uid":18553,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"81ecc88b9f3ebc916e21834c06b79888deb2c08d","tid":699745,"uid":58321,"like":707,"dislike":17,"score":690,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T19:22:53.000Z","msg":"屌無個留言係有建設性，個撚個都小學雞懶好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 戇撚鳩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T01:59:33.000Z","msg":"走囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bed4d74107b79e4b06dc0418e3cb1d5267903b3f","tid":699745,"uid":1666